------------------------------------------------------------
Potential Improvements
------------------------------------------------------------

- Add more stages to enhance segmentation accuracy:
  - Despeckling
  - Advanced thresholding methods
  - Edge smoothing
- These improvements would help generalize the algorithm to a broader range of microscopy images, as the current implementation may be overfitted to the sample dataset.
